# NudgingTool - demo manual HTTP tests
# Use with VSCode REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP Client.
#
# Flow:
# 1. Run "Get access token"
# 2. Run "imported_up [it]"
#
# Copy the access_token from "Get access token" into @accessToken manually.

